com.socrata.builders

Class ExternalDatasetBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.socrata.builders.AbstractDatasetInfoBuilder<ExternalDatasetBuilder,ExternalDataset>
      • com.socrata.builders.ExternalDatasetBuilder

  • public class ExternalDatasetBuilder
extends AbstractDatasetInfoBuilder<ExternalDatasetBuilder,ExternalDataset>
    Builds an external dataset that can be added to the server through the operations in SodaDDL for creating or updating a dataset. External dataset references are datasets that are not hosted by Socrata, but where Socrata provides a reference to another dataset.
